Here are some tips: 


 - Switching vibro on/off - tap phone menu button in main window; 


 - If you want immediatelly solve puzzle - tap phone menu button while playing and choose 'solve';


 - For hiding number in final solution while using Solver apps option tap 'Settings' and choose numbers you want hide;


 - You can create your own puzzles using "Solve for me" tools. Just create puzzle and check is it solveable?


 Have fun!
